      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t40",
      "x": 66,
      "y": 698,
      "text": "TRADEOFF:  +1-2 ms per Kafka write (2 ms \u2192 3 ms).  At 2K TPS, Kafka handles this easily.\nBENEFIT:  Zero tick loss, even during broker crashes.  No wrong candles, no stale Greeks, no missing market data.\nAlso enabled:  enable.idempotence=true,  retries=\u221e,  max.in.flight.requests.per.connection=5",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00"
    }
  ],
